{"type": "article", "id": 5160, "title": "Normann Copenhagen 酒具配件", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-13T08:00:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233427FGc3VlMIK9SfYeCy.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦设计品牌 Normann Copenhagen 最近推出了一系列品牌自有设计师 Simon Legald 设计的酒具配件，包括一款开瓶器、一个锡箔切割器、一个酒瓶塞以及一款倒酒器。Simon Legald 专注于每个单品最直接的功能，去除了不必要的设计，为 4 款单品设计了统一的镀钛不锈钢上部与硅胶材质的下部，镀钛涂层使得产品呈现出一种丝绸质感。据设计师介绍这两种材质都已被批准可用于食品配件。定价 37－46.25 美元（约合人民币 230－286 元）不等，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/families/basic\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233425U74CqMFs9fnlmitk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233425RitCqzjUE0oK1kds.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233426b3ynCzP59sYQGoi4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233426x31OYAuI85nXqR2Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233427EtrDMRKQOv7mug4p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}